Name: Coffeecompany
Review Text: This small coffee shop is very comfortable with sofas where you can sit. The coffee is really good. The choice if cakes and pastries is very limited. They are all good but if your goal is to eat something, it is not the right place to go to.

Name: Coffeecompany
Review Text: I like the overall atmosphere of this specific location. If you plan to study/work - they have a dedicated table specifically for that. Music is not too loud, and the coffee is decent. They have both espresso and filter coffees which you can pair with a delicious variety of snacks. Highly recommended
